een so far of the new Fear.<br>
<br>
All the regular mobs are the same, same level, same hitpoints, same spells and powers.  This is true from the spinechillers to the FFs.<br>
<br>
One new change to the regular mobs, Gorgons are now faster than SoW...one small feature that they added to enhance the quality of game play I bet.<br>
<br>
Drop rates of normal mobs are the same as they were before.<br>
<br>
We encountered a new mob last night, a corrupt golem, conned green to me, I charmed it and hailed it, nothing came of that.  We killed it, it dropped a bard flute, the one that normally came off of CT, congrats Rosi! =)<br>
<br>
Most importantly, the Safe Spot is still the same Safe Spot as before, so no need to change your plans in upcoming raids if you were planning on taking this route.<br>
<br>
The triplet golem named spawns seem have a longer spawn than 24 hours, they were not up last night after being killed by Enshadowed the day before, there did not seem to be any place holders for them either.<br>
<br>
I have no information on epic quest drops, we did not encounter any last night.<br>
<br>
That's all I have right now, feel free to add more as everyone goes up there more often. <p>Dauros 55th Enchanter of Ethos<BR>
